# netctl - Network diagnostics and monitoring

> macOS command-line utility (Rust)

## Project Overview

**Type:** Command-line utility (Rust)
**Purpose:** Network diagnostics and monitoring
**Platform:** macOS (Apple Silicon & Intel)

## Features

- Network interface statistics
- Bandwidth monitoring
- Connection tracking
- DNS resolution testing
- Latency and ping monitoring
- Network quality analysis

## Development

```bash
# Build
cargo build

# Run
cargo run -- [ARGS]

# Test
cargo test

# Format and lint
cargo fmt
cargo clippy

# Build release
cargo build --release
```

## Installation

```bash
# Install locally
cargo install --path .

# Build and copy to system
cargo build --release
cp target/release/netctl /usr/local/bin/
```

## Usage

```bash
# Show help
netctl --help

# Show version
netctl --version
```
